-- Bahrain Islamic Third-Quarter Loss Widens as Impairment Provisions Double
-- B y   A r i f   S h a r i f
-- 2010-10-20T04:48:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/bahrain-islamic-third-quarter-loss-widens-as-impairment-provisions-double.html
Bahrain Islamic Bank BSC said third-
quarter loss widened to 4.24 million dinars from 1.36 million
dinars a year earlier as impairment provisions rose.  Impairment provisions more than doubled to 4.3 million
dinars from 2 million dinars a year earlier, the bank said in a
statement to the Bahrain bourse today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
